<br>
I would say that character name is an important consideration.<br>
Our guild recently had an applicant, whose name turned me off immediately when I saw it in our &quot;candidate forum&quot;.  Fortunately, I didn't have to be faced with task of saying &quot;I don't want this fellow because of his/her name&quot; because he/she never did follow through on the application procedures.  Even so, having discussed the candidate with most of my guildmates his/her name gave them a bad feeling as well.<br>
